sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as Event Source
    participant R as EventHandlingRouter
    participant H as Target Handler

    S->>R: handle(event)
    R->>R: lookup by event.target
    alt Handler found
        R->>H: handle(event)
        H-->>R: Event (response event)
        R-->>S: Event
    else No handler
        R-->>S: HandlerNotFoundException
    end